Package de.gulden.application.jjack.clients

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cable
    JJack example client: Passes the audio signal through without any change.
    CableBeanInfo
    BeanInfo class for class Cable.
    Channel
    JJack example client: Selects one channel from a multi-channel input and routes it to the mono output channel #0.
    ChannelBeanInfo
    BeanInfo class for class Channel.
    Delay
    JJack example client: add an echo effect to the audio signal.
    DelayBeanInfo
    BeanInfo class for class Delay.
    Gain
    JJack example client: Change the audio volume.
    GainBeanInfo
    BeanInfo class for class Gain.
    Gate
    JJack example client: a noise gate that suppresses audio signal below a threshold value.
    GateBeanInfo
    BeanInfo class for class Gate.
    Oscilloscope
    JJack example client: Displays the audio waveform in realtime.
    OscilloscopeBeanInfo
    BeanInfo class for class Oscilloscope.
    Socket
    JJack example client: The starting point to connect clients to when building client sets inside a JavaBeans development environment.
    SocketBeanInfo
    BeanInfo class for class Socket.
    VU
    JJack example client: Displays the audio signal level as a chain of green, yellow and red LEDs.
    VUBeanInfo
    BeanInfo class for class VU.
